## ğŸª™ What is Bitcoin?

Bitcoin is a digital currency that allows peer-to-peer transactions without banks.  
It was invented by Satoshi Nakamoto in 2008 and introduced the concept of blockchain â€” a distributed ledger.

Bitcoin White Paper:  
https://bitcoin.org/bitcoin.pdf

